PRIVACY POLICY
SECTION 1 – Personal Information
The ASL kids app:
Does not collect any personally identifiable information from users.
Does not use any analytic software that tracks users.
Does not use your geographic location.
SECTION 2 – In-App Purchases
The ASL kids app contains In-App Purchases for additional content behind a parental gate.
SECTION
3 – Advertising
The ASL kids app does not include any advertisements or allow advertising companies to collect data from our app.
SECTION
4 – Links Within Apps
The ASL kids app:
Does not link to other websites.
Does not link to any social media networks.
QUESTIONS AND CONTACT INFORMATION
If you would like to: correct, register a complaint, or simply want more information contact our Privacy Compliance Officer at info@asl-kids.com